                  .and_then(exec("INSERT OR REPLACE INTO UserProfile (user_id, bio, avatar_url) VALUES (?, ?, ?)", 
                                 u.user_id.value, u.bio, u.avatar_url));
```

The `INSERT OR REPLACE` statement handles the upsert logic natively in SQLite, making it the most efficient solution.

